PN,43701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FThe UK's first deep geothermal plant
OL,8,Fgenerating power from heat miles
OL,9,Funderground ` and producing lithium
OL,10,Ffor car batteries ` has been switched
OL,11,Fon in Cornwall.
OL,13,FGeothermal Engineering Ltd (GEL)'s #50
OL,14,Fmillion United Downs site is set to
OL,15,Fdeliver renewable electricity around
OL,16,Fthe clock from the deepest well ever
OL,17,Fdrilled in the UK, at more than 5km (3
OL,18,Fmiles) deep.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FIt will draw up water at extremely
OL,8,Fhigh temperatures ` more than 190C `
OL,9,Fto drive turbines that will generate
OL,10,Fpower for 10,000 homes.
OL,12,FThe water also contains high
OL,13,Fconcentrations of lithium, which will
OL,14,Fbe extracted for the production of
OL,15,Fzero-carbon lithium carbonate, a key
OL,16,Fmaterial for electric car batteries
OL,17,Fand battery storage.
OL,19,FThe company said it will produce 100
OL,20,Ftonnes of lithium carbonate per year `
OL,21,Fenough to make 2,500 car batteries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FRyan Law, chief executive and founder
OL,8,Fof GEL, said there were plans to
OL,9,Fexpand the site and two other
OL,10,Fgeothermal energy projects in
OL,11,FCornwall, currently in the planning
OL,12,Fprocess, to produce enough lithium for
OL,13,F250,000 cars a year.
OL,15,FThe first site will produce 3
OL,16,Fmegawatts (MW) of power, with the
OL,17,Fthree projects generating up to 10MW
OL,18,Fof power, and Octopus Energy has
OL,19,Fsigned a long-term deal to purchase at
OL,20,Fleast 3MW of electricity, powering
OL,21,F10,000 homes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FDr Law said there was potential to
OL,8,Fexpand geothermal energy across the UK
OL,9,Fto provide large amounts of renewable
OL,10,Fpower.
OL,12,F"We're effectively tapping into a
OL,13,Fmassive nuclear power station that
OL,14,Fsomeone's already built," he said,
OL,15,Fadding, "the resource is gigantic".
OL,17,F"It's just people getting their heads
OL,18,Faround it ` you've got to start
OL,19,Fsomewhere and once you've started, it
OL,20,Fgets a lot easier."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@YO]wD@IOUwD@bO]yD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FHe said that while the plan to produce
OL,8,Fdeep geothermal electricity in
OL,9,FCornwall had been years in
OL,10,Fdevelopment, the company had not
OL,11,Fplanned to produce lithium, it was
OL,12,F"just lucky".
OL,14,F"Cornwall has been known for centuries
OL,15,Ffor, and used to have its wealth from,
OL,16,Fmining, so we knew it's got lots of
OL,17,Fminerals.
OL,19,F"When we tested the water in these
OL,20,Fvery deep wells, we found it is full
OL,21,Fof lithium.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,F"There are other minerals in there
OL,8,Fthat are also interesting, but lithium
OL,9,Fis a logical first choice because it
OL,10,Fgenuinely is a great resource and it's
OL,11,Fbetter than we've seen across the
OL,12,Fwhole of Europe.
OL,14,F"It's a very high concentration of
OL,15,Flithium and it's a very clean fluid,
OL,16,Fso it's a natural thing to do as a by-
OL,17,Fproduct from the power."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FDr Law said the power plant generates
OL,8,Fpower to process the lithium, while
OL,9,Fthe electricity generation process
OL,10,Falso cools the temperature of the
OL,11,Fliquid down to a level to be able to
OL,12,Fextract the lithium, and the whole
OL,13,Fplant has a very small surface
OL,14,Ffootprint.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FHe also warned there was a need to
OL,8,Fscale up the supply chains for
OL,9,Fcritical minerals such as lithium in
OL,10,FEurope, and said there should be a
OL,11,F"green national premium" price for
OL,12,Fzero-carbon, domestically-produced
OL,13,Fproducts to drive the market to reduce
OL,14,Freliance on imports from places such
OL,15,Fas China.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FDr Alan Whitehead, Department for
OL,8,FEnergy Security and Net Zero Minister,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The UK's first ever geothermal
OL,10,Fpower is a ground-breaking moment for
OL,11,FUK energy innovation, powering
OL,12,Fthousands of homes with clean,
OL,13,Fhomegrown power.
OL,15,F"With zerocarbon lithium now being
OL,16,Fproduced here in the UK, British
OL,17,Fbusinesses are leading the way in
OL,18,Fsecuring the materials needed to power
OL,19,Fthe next generation of electric cars."
OL,26,@qD@GOUwD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,FThe electricity from the geothermal
OL,8,Fplant has secured a "contract for
OL,9,Fdifference" for renewable power, which
OL,10,Fmeans it will receive a fixed price
OL,11,Ffor the energy it provides to the
OL,12,Fgrid, of #119 per megawatt hour (in
OL,13,F2012 prices).
OL,15,FGreg Jackson, founder of Octopus
OL,16,FEnergy, said: "Bills are still too
OL,17,Fhigh, and the answer is more
OL,18,Fhomegrown, renewable energy.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@KO]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772209190
OL,3,CUK's first geothermal plant in
OL,4,CCornwall will power homes and produce
OL,5,Clithium
OL,7,F"For the first time, we're bringing
OL,8,Fdeep geothermal power to British homes
OL,9,F` a clean, constant energy source
OL,10,Fright beneath our feet.
OL,12,F"Projects like United Downs show how
OL,13,Fthe UK can cut bills and carbon by
OL,14,Ftapping every ounce of our renewable
OL,15,Fpotential."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
